{"tid":947502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 廣東淪陷 珠海爆非洲豬瘟疫情","createTime":"2018-12-19T10:09:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T05:18:36.000Z","uid":54373,"like":121,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"9a71d7d0d87a6c4da4f317f6680be45375110f1f","tid":947502,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T10:09:50.000Z","msg":"國家農業農村部新聞辦公室周三（19日）表示，廣東省於珠海市香洲區爆發首例非洲豬瘟疫情。<br />\n<br />\n國家農業農村部於周三下午3時接獲中國動物疫病預防控制中心報告，經中國動物衛生與流行病學中心（國家外來動物疫病研究中心）確診，廣東省珠海市香洲區一屠宰場發生非洲豬瘟疫情。截至目前，該屠宰場同批待宰生豬50隻，發病11隻，死亡11隻。<br />\n<br />\n當地已按照要求啟動應急回應機制，採取封鎖、撲殺、無害化處理、消毒等處置措施，對全部病死和撲殺豬進行無害化處理。同時，禁止所有生豬及其產品調出封鎖區，禁止生豬運入封鎖區。"},{"pid":"ff0bf2334dacbb9c2e5d5deb30fca0c02f435a92","tid":947502,"uid":198583,"like":58,"dislike":4,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T10:15:29.000Z","msg":"好耶<br />\n<br />\n禍亂開始了<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b427fdf908aef17daa63bb5ab4d99ce479c8a6ee","tid":947502,"uid":158270,"like":5,"dislike":8,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T10:21:49.000Z","msg":"Link"},{"pid":"eeb370b5559a4e12a5310ca70b256d68adaf9265","tid":947502,"uid":54373,"like":6,"dislike":65,"score":-59,"quote":{"pid":"b427fdf908aef17daa63bb5ab4d99ce479c8a6ee","tid":947502,"uid":158270,"like":5,"dislike":8,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T10:21:49.000Z","msg":"Link"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T10:30:19.000Z","msg":"食屎啦，抻手黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n是旦copy一段google已出晒啦"},{"pid":"9707f1bb592748488970c965774916f7e7947566","tid":947502,"uid":51701,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T10:31:22.000Z","msg":"Link"},{"pid":"9b8be43701fa11fb242bb7ba2003672a143680cb","tid":947502,"uid":550,"like":118,"dislike":0,"score":118,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T10:31:23.000Z","msg":"楊永強當年都話香港冇肺炎爆發<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n查咗幾耐先知源頭係廣州教授<br />\n香港人自求多福<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.